{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1636,"text":"What makes a great leader today?"},{"time":5231,"text":"Many of us carry this image"},{"time":7874,"text":"of this all-knowing superhero"},{"time":11194,"text":"who stands and commands"},{"time":13642,"text":"and protects his followers."},{"time":17271,"text":"But that's kind of an image from another time,"},{"time":21567,"text":"and what's also outdated"},{"time":23818,"text":"are the leadership development programs"},{"time":26220,"text":"that are based on success models"},{"time":28603,"text":"for a world that was, not a world that is"},{"time":32785,"text":"or that is coming."}]},{"cues":[{"time":34949,"text":"We conducted a study of 4,000 companies,"},{"time":39360,"text":"and we asked them, let's see the effectiveness"},{"time":42367,"text":"of your leadership development programs."},{"time":44958,"text":"Fifty-eight percent of the companies"},{"time":47146,"text":"cited significant talent gaps"},{"time":49514,"text":"for critical leadership roles."},{"time":51869,"text":"That means that despite\ncorporate training programs,"},{"time":55308,"text":"off-sites, assessments, coaching, all of these things,"},{"time":59745,"text":"more than half the companies"},{"time":61686,"text":"had failed to grow enough great leaders."},{"time":66543,"text":"You may be asking yourself,"},{"time":68566,"text":"is my company helping me to prepare"},{"time":71297,"text":"to be a great 21st-century leader?"},{"time":74540,"text":"The odds are, probably not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":77952,"text":"Now, I've spent 25 years of my professional life"},{"time":82015,"text":"observing what makes great leaders."},{"time":85520,"text":"I've worked inside Fortune 500 companies,"},{"time":87985,"text":"I've advised over 200 CEOs,"},{"time":90054,"text":"and I've cultivated more leadership pipelines"},{"time":92813,"text":"than you can imagine."},{"time":95823,"text":"But a few years ago, I noticed a disturbing trend"},{"time":99548,"text":"in leadership preparation."},{"time":102763,"text":"I noticed that, despite all the efforts,"},{"time":106589,"text":"there were familiar stories that kept resurfacing"},{"time":109128,"text":"about individuals."},{"time":111252,"text":"One story was about Chris,"},{"time":114886,"text":"a high-potential, superstar leader"},{"time":117230,"text":"who moves to a new unit and fails,"},{"time":120832,"text":"destroying unrecoverable value."},{"time":123568,"text":"And then there were stories like Sidney, the CEO,"},{"time":127161,"text":"who was so frustrated"},{"time":128863,"text":"because her company is cited"},{"time":130930,"text":"as a best company for leaders,"},{"time":133259,"text":"but only one of the top 50 leaders is equipped"},{"time":137096,"text":"to lead their crucial initiatives."},{"time":139681,"text":"And then there were stories"},{"time":141638,"text":"like the senior leadership team"},{"time":144168,"text":"of a once-thriving business"},{"time":146248,"text":"that's surprised by a market shift,"},{"time":149704,"text":"finds itself having to force the company"},{"time":152435,"text":"to reduce its size in half"},{"time":154763,"text":"or go out of business."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157576,"text":"Now, these recurring stories"},{"time":160294,"text":"cause me to ask two questions."},{"time":162861,"text":"Why are the leadership gaps widening"},{"time":165332,"text":"when there's so much more investment"},{"time":167265,"text":"in leadership development?"},{"time":169489,"text":"And what are the great leaders doing"},{"time":172786,"text":"distinctly different to thrive and grow?"},{"time":176661,"text":"One of the things that I did,"},{"time":179030,"text":"I was so consumed by these questions"},{"time":181706,"text":"and also frustrated by those stories,"},{"time":184650,"text":"that I left my job"},{"time":187058,"text":"so that I could study this full time,"},{"time":189638,"text":"and I took a year to travel"},{"time":192583,"text":"to different parts of the world"},{"time":194603,"text":"to learn about effective and ineffective"},{"time":196989,"text":"leadership practices in companies,"},{"time":199374,"text":"countries and nonprofit organizations."},{"time":202877,"text":"And so I did things like travel to South Africa,"},{"time":206204,"text":"where I had an opportunity to understand"},{"time":209130,"text":"how Nelson Mandela was ahead of his time"},{"time":211604,"text":"in anticipating and navigating"},{"time":213495,"text":"his political, social and economic context."},{"time":216912,"text":"I also met a number of nonprofit leaders"},{"time":219935,"text":"who, despite very limited financial resources,"},{"time":223905,"text":"were making a huge impact in the world,"},{"time":226848,"text":"often bringing together seeming adversaries."},{"time":230710,"text":"And I spent countless hours in presidential libraries"},{"time":235765,"text":"trying to understand how the environment"},{"time":238097,"text":"had shaped the leaders,"},{"time":239255,"text":"the moves that they made,"},{"time":240858,"text":"and then the impact of those moves"},{"time":242384,"text":"beyond their tenure."},{"time":245311,"text":"And then, when I returned to work full time,"},{"time":248312,"text":"in this role, I joined with wonderful colleagues"},{"time":251601,"text":"who were also interested in these questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255093,"text":"Now, from all this, I distilled"},{"time":258038,"text":"the characteristics of leaders who are thriving"},{"time":262042,"text":"and what they do differently,"},{"time":263868,"text":"and then I also distilled"},{"time":266321,"text":"the preparation practices that enable people"},{"time":269263,"text":"to grow to their potential."},{"time":271919,"text":"I want to share some of those with you now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":273852,"text":"(\"What makes a great leader in the 21st century?\")"}]},{"cues":[{"time":275927,"text":"In a 21st-century world, which is more global,"},{"time":279292,"text":"digitally enabled and transparent,"},{"time":281743,"text":"with faster speeds of information \nflow and innovation,"},{"time":285156,"text":"and where nothing big gets done"},{"time":287451,"text":"without some kind of a complex matrix,"},{"time":290687,"text":"relying on traditional development practices"},{"time":294347,"text":"will stunt your growth as a leader."},{"time":297005,"text":"In fact, traditional assessments"},{"time":299852,"text":"like narrow 360 surveys or\noutdated performance criteria"},{"time":304195,"text":"will give you false positives,"},{"time":306233,"text":"lulling you into thinking that you are more prepared"},{"time":309659,"text":"than you really are."},{"time":311799,"text":"Leadership in the 21st century is defined"},{"time":315692,"text":"and evidenced by three questions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":318846,"text":"Where are you looking"},{"time":320180,"text":"to anticipate the next change"},{"time":323256,"text":"to your business model or your life?"},{"time":326729,"text":"The answer to this question is on your calendar."},{"time":331579,"text":"Who are you spending time with? On what topics?"},{"time":335520,"text":"Where are you traveling? What are you reading?"},{"time":338068,"text":"And then how are you distilling this"},{"time":339815,"text":"into understanding potential discontinuities,"},{"time":343522,"text":"and then making a decision to do something"},{"time":345774,"text":"right now so that you're prepared and ready?"},{"time":350188,"text":"There's a leadership team that does a practice"},{"time":353190,"text":"where they bring together each member"},{"time":356162,"text":"collecting, here are trends that impact me,"},{"time":358969,"text":"here are trends that impact another team member,"},{"time":361254,"text":"and they share these,"},{"time":362653,"text":"and then make decisions,\nto course-correct a strategy"},{"time":365449,"text":"or to anticipate a new move."},{"time":368706,"text":"Great leaders are not head-down."},{"time":371759,"text":"They see around corners,"},{"time":374004,"text":"shaping their future, not just reacting to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377913,"text":"The second question is,"},{"time":379868,"text":"what is the diversity measure"},{"time":381887,"text":"of your personal and professional\nstakeholder network?"},{"time":385506,"text":"You know, we hear often about \ngood ol' boy networks"},{"time":388508,"text":"and they're certainly alive and \nwell in many institutions."},{"time":392424,"text":"But to some extent, we all have a network"},{"time":394967,"text":"of people that we're comfortable with."},{"time":396896,"text":"So this question is about your capacity"},{"time":399808,"text":"to develop relationships with people"},{"time":402307,"text":"that are very different than you."},{"time":403830,"text":"And those differences can be biological,"},{"time":406823,"text":"physical, functional, political, \ncultural, socioeconomic."},{"time":411607,"text":"And yet, despite all these differences,"},{"time":415050,"text":"they connect with you"},{"time":416807,"text":"and they trust you enough"},{"time":418061,"text":"to cooperate with you"},{"time":419343,"text":"in achieving a shared goal."},{"time":422481,"text":"Great leaders understand"},{"time":424816,"text":"that having a more diverse network"},{"time":427745,"text":"is a source of pattern identification"},{"time":431286,"text":"at greater levels and also of solutions,"},{"time":434071,"text":"because you have people that are thinking"},{"time":435895,"text":"differently than you are."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438580,"text":"Third question: are you courageous enough"},{"time":441930,"text":"to abandon a practice that has \nmade you successful in the past?"},{"time":447832,"text":"There's an expression: Go along to get along."},{"time":451981,"text":"But if you follow this advice,"},{"time":454899,"text":"chances are as a leader,"},{"time":457291,"text":"you're going to keep doing\nwhat's familiar and comfortable."},{"time":461806,"text":"Great leaders dare to be different."},{"time":464659,"text":"They don't just talk about risk-taking,"},{"time":466304,"text":"they actually do it."},{"time":468122,"text":"And one of the leaders shared with me the fact that"},{"time":471034,"text":"the most impactful development comes"},{"time":473611,"text":"when you are able to build the emotional stamina"},{"time":476915,"text":"to withstand people telling you that your new idea"},{"time":481075,"text":"is naïve or reckless or just plain stupid."},{"time":485793,"text":"Now interestingly, the people who will join you"},{"time":489655,"text":"are not your usual suspects in your network."},{"time":493110,"text":"They're often people that think differently"},{"time":496761,"text":"and therefore are willing to join you"},{"time":499633,"text":"in taking a courageous leap."},{"time":501992,"text":"And it's a leap, not a step."},{"time":505243,"text":"More than traditional leadership programs,"},{"time":508152,"text":"answering these three questions"},{"time":510034,"text":"will determine your effectiveness"},{"time":511417,"text":"as a 21st-century leader."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514886,"text":"So what makes a great leader in the 21st century?"},{"time":519307,"text":"I've met many, and they stand out."},{"time":522856,"text":"They are women and men"},{"time":524507,"text":"who are preparing themselves"},{"time":526273,"text":"not for the comfortable predictability of yesterday"},{"time":529392,"text":"but also for the realities of today"},{"time":533168,"text":"and all of those unknown possibilities of tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":537429,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":539856,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}